Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚倒在了正门口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  早餐做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  九澄同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无变化的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着大镰刀的杀人鬼少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的真面目居然是…栉名田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.64,0:01:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  快回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就到上课时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后图书室见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？栉名田请假了吗  真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:41.84,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.94,0:03:45.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}丧失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  拉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  身体又不舒服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这里总是拉不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这里呀  像这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我想听香织姐姐的示范演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是那份名单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你才把名单交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要泄露出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这镇子原本就不需要那些人的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但偏偏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  并不是指你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用在意  我只是打杂的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成工作了就立刻从这里消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的事是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还需要去接麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有些事想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来还想听听伯父的意见的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于嫦娥狼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神原本是本地人敬拜的土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说从前这一带生活着狼群
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神化身成狼并守护着城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得之前和博士君的父亲说的…大神和嫦娥狼的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说山里还有嫦娥狼生存着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是大型野生动物能够悄然生存的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大神传说还流传着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫦娥狼就会继续生存下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了这样的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我更觉得是恰好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过大神的信仰和传说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩盖了至今仍生存着的嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那嫦娥狼现在还存在着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但那也许和我们所想的狼是不同的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是传说以前生活在这一带的大型狼——嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是越是调查它的真相就越是模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能证明它存在过的证据太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说  嫦娥镇以外的地方都不承认其存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个我个人的假设
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许嫦娥狼和普通的狼是完全不同的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如是拥有人类般智慧的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人狼之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为凶月  带来不幸的红色月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  不吉利的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道彗星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同样被当作不吉利的象征的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如传言中数年后将要到来的哈雷彗星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是不吉利的象征之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻它是会带来疾病的凶星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那彗星一样被当作不吉利的象征的  就是凶月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天的气温和湿度都比以往要高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闷热的天气持续到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以特产的八朔也收获不济
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做各种调查的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了含有嫦娥狼和凶月这些关键词的「嫦娥数数歌」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的超自然魂告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些歌词里一定隐藏着什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也是常有的设定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  我现在打算去地方资料馆调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  对了  如果找到嫦娥数数歌的歌词的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能听取下伯父的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  会告诉他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又偷懒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最开始学习不是挺认真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授都夸奖你很勤奋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在却人不像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得地质学没意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和刚才说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家很贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃饭就得花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此必须要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你又是为了什么来到大学的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老在外面吃饭也不考虑下花费  还喊穷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做饭不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑脸我真的觉得很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来打个招呼多好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真没想到您还会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前就这么觉得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.31,0:11:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生的笑脸一定很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  刚才的音色真好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还远远不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来想去东京的音大认真学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么不去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不能离开这座城镇所以放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  今天来学习小提琴的学生烤了蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起来品尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要为三重子复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人好像回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:12:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  麻奈做的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？我为了香织姐姐努力做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我们就开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:12:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小眠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子  我们已经在「中心」保护起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  我想查一下「嫦娥数数歌」的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数数歌啊  请稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数数歌…  数数歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  在里面的D13号书架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤月盈盈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨镰下矣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「落神」的仪式…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  我是九澄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  麻奈她的话  已经被令尊接走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是刚好错过了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才该道歉呢  来得这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说谎  请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的  的确是在这里  一个女人拿着巨大的镰刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座小镇里  有着充满了谜团的杀人集团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.18,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你现在方便么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也见过杀人现场？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过那已经是四年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:15:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我也和你一样  想去报警
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可警局却空无一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人现场也消失得无影无踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个被杀的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新珠三重子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩在同一所大学读书
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为了写毕业论文  而造访了这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却万万没有想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而至于当时那不知底细的杀人集团…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个杀人集团之中  拿着巨型镰刀的少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们班上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田眠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  这些话  反正也不会有人信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法向任何人谈起这事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  我想  如果是你的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话  一定是能够相信我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我说…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫贤木俊一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤木先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢…  欢迎回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去香织小姐那儿去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果说她已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是洋葱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈  我能进来么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸他好担…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.16,0:17:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织姐姐她说  从今天开始  不准备再教我拉小提琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香织小姐她…  没有说原因么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是因为身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因为看到大姐姐她有时无精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想多陪陪她的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.29,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  我也很担心香织小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆下回就不以上课的名义  而是去探望她如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人么？  有人在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有人在么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喊破喉咙也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.27,0:18:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.66,0:18:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是那样么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那样」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问你是不是也成了「神人」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是你的恋人？  还是你喜欢的对象？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  你的对象  也像摘花前辈那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘花前辈  是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚大哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  非常喜欢前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他能够给我一个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我被送到了这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神人」是指什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  你还没有听说么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  为人身  而又非人之存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没窗子对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这里应该是地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下雨  排水沟中的流水声  就从天花板上传来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的那位摘花前辈他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于戒律所定的「落神之式」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落神？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个说法  就是被处决了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为「神人」的前辈  和我接了吻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我便不再为人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为人身  而非人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上现在  也对气味非常敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:21:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  和我不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是「神人」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上  有着「神堕人」的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:17.94,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:17.94,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:28.65,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが信じた愛の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:28.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信之情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.91,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱きしめた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.80,0:22:34.91,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:37.77,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影が月でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:37.77,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影非月  月非影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:41.15,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:41.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:49.72,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}戸惑いの月が満ちる　融ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:49.72,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}盈惑月  消无痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.57,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつものこころが　君を縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:56.57,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结若缚君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:07.18,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}堕ちて行く決意が許されるまで　愛なのと信じたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:07.18,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}则深信此爱  直至神允  坠天之志
